 <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">Gap structure of 1D cut and project Hamiltonians</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We study the gap properties of nearest neighbors tight binding models on quasiperiodic chains. We argue that two kind of gaps should be distinguished: stable and transient. We show that stable gaps have a well defined quasiperiodic limit. We also show that there is a direct relation between the gap size and the gap label.</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
